  "story": "A heartfelt thanksgiving keerthanam known across all Kerala church denominations. This simple yet powerful hymn of gratitude is often sung at the close of worship services and thanksgiving gatherings. Its warm melody and repetitive refrain make it a favorite among all age groups, from children to elders.",
  "lyrics": {
